Interface Status

public interface Status

This class represents the StatusType complex type in SAML protocol schema.

   <complexContent>

         <element ref="{urn:oasis:names:tc:SAML:2.0:protocol}StatusDetail" minOccurs="0"/>
       </sequence>
     </restriction>
   </complexContent>
 </complexType>
